r poster by the electronic poster upload deadline (May 18).<\/dd>\n<dt>Important Dates for Poster<\/dt>\n<dd>\n<table class=\"plain\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Submission Deadline<\/td>\n<td><s>Apr. 27 (23:59)<\/s><br \/>\n\u2192 May 14 (23:59) <strong style=\"color: #c00\">(extended)<\/strong><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Author Notification<\/td>\n<td><s>May 7<\/s><br \/>\n\u2192 As needed <strong style=\"color: #c00\">(extended)<\/strong><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Electronic Poster Upload Deadline<\/td>\n<td>May 18 (23:59)<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Poster Session<\/td>\n<td colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"\/2018\/program\/\">May 29<\/a><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<\/dd>\n<\/dl>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Call for Posters xSIG 2018 solicits poster presentations from a wide range of fields such as: research of any  <a class=\"read-more\" href=\"https:\/\/xsig.ipsj.or.jp\/2018\/en\/cf\/posters.html\">Read More<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3,"featured_media":0,"parent":17,"menu_order":2,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/xsig.ipsj.or.jp\/2018\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/457"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/xsig.ipsj.or.jp\/2018\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/xsig.ipsj.or.jp\/2018\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/xsig.ipsj.or.jp\/2018\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/xsig.ipsj.or.jp\/2018\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=457"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/xsig.ipsj.or.jp\/2018\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/457\/revisions"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/xsig.ipsj.or.jp\/2018\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/17"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/xsig.ipsj.or.jp\/2018\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=457"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}